0" alt="How many standards are in the Care Certificate - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="How many standards are in the Care Certificate - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-leSONj uTJGF pf-15_"/></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-7c9a" data-category="Generic Content" data-name="Matcha" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-jNHqnW kXSKNz pf-16_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-cqJhZP gRKDwp"><div class="sc-iAKWXU lesjfG pf-17_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:0px;--s-sm:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eySxxw fIKYYX pf-18_"><p class="sc-dMOJrz cGFGtP pf-19_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjztik hIbmEr pf-21_">The Care Certificate is a set of standards designed to ensure excellence in health and social care. It is a crucial requirement for individuals new to the sector, providing them with the necessary knowledge and skills to deliver compassionate, safe, high-quality care and support. This blog will explore how many standards are included in the <a href="https://www.mandatorytraining.co.uk/products/care-certificate-train-the-trainer-trainer-pack-cpduk-accredited?variant=31839814582341" target="_blank"><i><span style="color: rgb(0, 102, 204);">Care Certificate</span></i></a> and why they are so important.</span></p><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-jeraig eTNnJl pf-22_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjztik hIbmEr pf-24_">Understanding the Care Certificate</span></h2><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Understanding_the_Care_Certificate_-_number_of_standards_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1692798340" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Understanding_the_Care_Certificate_-_number_of_standards_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1692798340 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Understanding_the_Care_Certificate_-_number_of_standards_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.jpg?v=1692798340 320w" width="2000" height="1125" alt="Understanding the Care Certificate - number of standards - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Understanding the Care Certificate - number of standards - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-leSONj uTJGF pf-25_"/><p class="sc-dMOJrz cGFGtP pf-26_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjztik hIbmEr pf-28_">Before we delve into the specifics of the Care Certificate, let's define what it is and why it matters. The Care Certificate is designed for the non-regulated health and social care workforce, ensuring that everyone has the same foundational skills, knowledge, and behaviours required to provide quality care and support. The Certificate, developed by a partnership between Health Education England, Skills for Health and Skills for Care, establishes a set of standards for health and social care workers. It has been deemed the benchmark for induction by the Care Quality Commission (CQC), ensuring a baseline of skills and knowledge. </span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-jeraig eTNnJl pf-29_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjztik hIbmEr pf-31_">The structure of the Care Certificate </span></h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/The_structure_of_the_Care_Certificate_-_train_the_trainer_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1692798425" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/The_structure_of_the_Care_Certificate_-_train_the_trainer_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1692798425 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/The_structure_of_the_Care_Certificate_-_train_the_trainer_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.jpg?v=1692798425 320w" width="1872" height="1248" alt="The structure of the Care Certificate - train the trainer - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="The structure of the Care Certificate - train the trainer - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-leSONj uTJGF pf-32_"/><p class="sc-dMOJrz cGFGtP pf-33_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjztik hIbmEr pf-35_">The Care Certificate consists of a set of fifteen minimum standards, each focusing on a specific area of knowledge or skill required in the health and social care sector. These fifteen standards include: </span></p><div class="sc-iAKWXU lesjfG pf-36_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eySxxw fIKYYX pf-37_"><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:10px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-eZhRLC dwDNfh pf-38_"><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-dYtuZ fhpFsJ pf-39_">Understand your role</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-dYtuZ fhpFsJ pf-41_">Your personal development</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-dYtuZ fhpFsJ pf-43_">Duty of care</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-dYtuZ fhpFsJ pf-45_">Equality and diversity</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-dYtuZ fhpFsJ pf-47_">Work in a person-centred way</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-dYtuZ fhpFsJ pf-49_">Communication</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-dYtuZ fhpFsJ pf-51_">Privacy and dignity</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-dYtuZ fhpFsJ pf-53_">Fluids and nutrition</li></ul></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eySxxw fIKYYX pf-55_"><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:10px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-eZhRLC dwDNfh pf-56_"><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-dYtuZ fhpFsJ pf-57_">9.&nbsp;Awareness of mental health, dementia, and learning disabilities</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-dYtuZ fhpFsJ pf-59_">10.&nbsp;Safeguarding adults and children</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-dYtuZ fhpFsJ pf-61_">11.&nbsp;Basic life support</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-dYtuZ fhpFsJ pf-63_">12.&nbsp;Health and safety</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-dYtuZ fhpFsJ pf-65_">13.&nbsp;Handling information</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-dYtuZ fhpFsJ pf-67_">14.&nbsp;Infection prevention and control</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-dYtuZ fhpFsJ pf-69_">15.&nbsp;Dementia Awareness</li></ul></div></div></div><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-jeraig eTNnJl pf-71_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjztik hIbmEr pf-73_">Emphasising the importance of each standard</span></h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Emphasising_the_importance_of_each_standard_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1692798518" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Emphasising_the_importance_of_each_standard_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1692798518 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Emphasising_the_importance_of_each_standard_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.jpg?v=1692798518 320w" width="1900" height="1267" alt="Emphasising the importance of each standard - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Emphasising the importance of each standard - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-leSONj uTJGF pf-74_"/><p class="sc-dMOJrz cGFGtP pf-75_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjztik hIbmEr pf-77_">Each standard included in the Care Certificate is vital in ensuring quality care and support. Understanding one's role, for example, is crucial in establishing a strong foundation for effective care provision. Promoting equality and diversity ensures that individuals from diverse backgrounds receive equal access to care and support. Person-centred care places the individual at the heart of their care journey, while effective communication fosters collaboration and trust. Duty of care is a legal requirement. Safeguarding adults and children is critical in the health and social care sector, protecting vulnerable individuals from abuse and harm. These are just a few examples of how each standard plays a vital role in ensuring quality care and support.</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-jeraig eTNnJl pf-78_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjztik hIbmEr pf-80_">Training of the Care Certificate</span></h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Training_of_the_Care_Certificate_-_train_the_trainer_pack_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_8d0534cf-e0d8-4357-8675-e705b7b0e66a.jpg?v=1692798646" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Training_of_the_Care_Certificate_-_train_the_trainer_pack_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_8d0534cf-e0d8-4357-8675-e705b7b0e66a.jpg?v=1692798646 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Training_of_the_Care_Certificate_-_train_the_trainer_pack_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_8d0534cf-e0d8-4357-8675-e705b7b0e66a_500x.jpg?v=1692798646 320w" width="2240" height="1493" alt="Training of the Care Certificate - train the trainer pack - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Training of the Care Certificate - train the trainer pack - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-leSONj uTJGF pf-81_"/><p class="sc-bvFjSx yVjXo pf-82_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Becoming a trainer of the Care Certificate offers the opportunity to make a difference, share expertise, enhance career prospects and contribute to the growth of the health and social care sector. If youâ€™re looking to train your new staff and have a desire to improve the quality of care, becoming a Care Certificate trainer may be a fulfilling and rewarding path to pursue. To become a trainer, you need to have knowledge and expertise in the subject matter and the ability to teach it effectively. Fortunately, the trainer pack provides structure and guidance to help you with training and workshop organisation. Upon completion of the training, you become an accredited trainer, complete with a <a href="https://cpduk.co.uk/providers/the-mandatory-training-group" target="_blank"><i><span style="color: rgb(0, 102, 204);">CPDUK-accredited</span></i></a> certificate.<br><br>The train-the-trainer model offers many advantages, including its affordability. One of the most significant benefits of this approach is access to a Learning Management System, which is not available in traditional in-learning training programs.<br> </p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-jeraig eTNnJl pf-84_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-bjztik hIbmEr pf-86_">Increase your compliance rating </span></h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Increase_your_compliance_rating_-_care_certificate_standards_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1692798733" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Increase_your_compliance_rating_-_care_certificate_standards_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1692798733 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Increase_your_compliance_rating_-_care_certificate_standards_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.jpg?v=1692798733 320w" width="2000" height="1334" alt="Increase your compliance rating - care certificate standards - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Increase your compliance rating - care certificate standards - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-leSONj uTJGF pf-87_"/><p c